##blue|**Vincent Bohart##:** Well done everyone, I'm proud of you all. 

##orange|**Noah Patel##:** Thank you, sir I--

##blue|**Vincent Bohart##:** Is what I would say if you hadn't all fucked this up. Jesus Christ, people. I didn't expect a miracle, but this? 

##blue|**Vincent Bohart##:** All I ask is that you spend one week doing your jobs, and what do I see: misallocation of site resources, incompetence, insubordination, and a damn novel draft; Noah if I wanted to read that I wouldn't have thrown away the earlier manuscripts you gave me. 

##orange|**Noah Patel##:** You said a bird-- 

##blue|**Vincent Bohart##:** We've got five hours left to get shit done till RAISA kicks in our door and my teeth. So if you've got any ideas, now is the time people. 

##orange|**Noah Patel##:** ...

##red|**Tony Catalano##:**...

##green|**Leonora Morales##:**...

